text: Arthur Whitling (5 June 1892 – 8 January 1967) was an Australian rules footballer who played for the Collingwood Football Club in the Victorian Football League (VFL). == Notes == == External links == * *Arthur Whitling's profile at Collingwood Forever Category:1892 births Category:1967 deaths Category:Australian rules footballers from Victoria (Australia) Category:Collingwood Football Club players Category:Australian military personnel of World War I
